nodes.bodyText:
Why I excluded the first line from the common prefix:
SomeGrammarRule: 
  {NewThingy} ('{'
    elements+=Element;
  '}');

When you look at the group in parentheses, you'd want to strip the leading space from the last two lines but the element doesn't have a leading space in the first line. I didn't check the current approach carefully though it might indeed be flawed to exclude line zero.

